Time Team (History Documentary) 

Time - 17:45 - 18:45 (1 hour long) 

When - Sunday 16th March on Channel 4 

8,000 Tonnes of Stone: Hamsterley, County Durham. 

Tony Robinson, Mick Aston, Phil Harding and the team are in County Durham to investigate a truly massive stone structure that has baffled people for centuries. Known locally as The Castles, its five-metre thick walls enclose a space the size of a football pitch.
